WEBVTT

00:06.040 --> 00:08.208
- Roth of the Mere.
- Your husband

00:08.233 --> 00:10.160
promised us iron weapons.

00:10.200 --> 00:13.240
However, they must not be
simply a gift, but a dowry.

00:13.280 --> 00:15.560
A marriage between my son
and his daughter

00:15.600 --> 00:17.600
will make our alliance stronger.

00:17.640 --> 00:20.200
You'll go to Mere.
And take Elvina with you.

00:20.240 --> 00:22.160
- Why?
- She knows their ways,

00:22.200 --> 00:24.360
and you will forget her now.

00:28.840 --> 00:31.120
- Did you see something?
- It's nothing.

00:31.160 --> 00:33.520
You're behind all this.
You wanted to be Jarl,

00:33.560 --> 00:36.320
but you didn't want to be seen
to betray your own sister.

00:36.360 --> 00:37.800
Vlade was your man.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.074
